UID:http://calagator.org/events/1250482497
DESCRIPTION:🎉 We're throwing open the doors\, and it's time to celebrate!
  UpStart Collective is officially moving into our new home at **Big Pink
 ** — one of Portland's most iconic buildings — and we want you there to 
 kick things off with us on the 5th floor.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Come raise a g
 lass (or a coffee cup) with Josh and the rest of the crew as we toast to
  new beginnings\, fresh space\, and everything that's ahead. Whether you
 've been with us from the start or you're just now hearing about UpStart
  Collective\, this is the perfect moment to walk through the door\, look
  around\, and feel what we're building together.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​We'll s
 tart the morning off right with a ribbon-cutting with Portland Mayor\, K
 eith Wilson. After that\, we'll have programming from our partners at Pl
 ug and Play and the Komputational Kulture team.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Swing by
  on the morning of **April 8th**\, take in the views from the 5th floor\
 , and help us make some noise in our new space. See you at Big Pink! 🩷\n
 \nTags: free\, founders\, Big Pink\, networking\, startups\n\nImported f
 rom: http://calagator.org/events/1250482497
URL:https://luma.com/ul04ns8a
SUMMARY:UpStart Collective: Grand Opening Day @ Big Pink!
LOCATION:U.S. Bancorp Tower (Big Pink): 111 Southwest 5th Avenue\, Portla
 nd OR 97204 US
SEQUENCE:1
END:VEVENT
