DESCRIPTION:This event runs from Thursday\, May 28\, 2026 at 9am through 
 Friday\, May 29\, 2026 at 4pm.\n\nDescription:\n&quot\;DigiMarCon Great 
 Lakes – The #1 Digital Marketing\, Media and Advertising Conference in t
 he Great Lakes Region.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nGet ready to be inspired and infor
 med at DigiMarCon Great Lakes\, the premier annual conference for digita
 l marketing\, media\, advertising and business professionals in the Grea
 t Lakes region\, returning May 28-29\, 2026 to The Ritz-Carlton Clevelan
 d Hotel in Cleveland\, Ohio. Experience two action-packed days including
  keynotes\, master classes and panels from experts and thought leaders w
 ith cutting-edge strategies and numerous networking opportunities. Atten
 d in-person or online to access the next wave of digital innovation\, in
 cluding insights in AI and ChatGPT\, marketing automation\, content crea
 tion\, growth hacking\, social media marketing\, SEO\, and more.&#13\;\n
 &#13\;\nHighlights:&#13\;\n     •   Top Industry Keynotes: Hear from vis
 ionary speakers who push the boundaries of digital marketing.&#13\;\n   
   •   Networking Opportunities: Connect with thought leaders\, reunite w
 ith your peers\, and expand your professional network.&#13\;\n     •   H
 ands-On Learning: Master classes\, case studies\, and strategy sessions 
 to equip you with practical solutions for immediate impact.&#13\;\n&#13\
 ;\nThis year’s edition will feature topics such as:&#13\;\n     •   Arti
 ficial Intelligence\, ChatGPT\, and Marketing Automation&#13\;\n     •  
  Content Marketing\, Email Marketing\, Social Media Marketing\, and Infl
 uencer Marketing&#13\;\n     •   Conversion Rate Optimization\, Mobile M
 arketing\, and Video Marketing&#13\;\n     •   Data Science\, Big Data\,
  Programmatic Advertising and Predictive Analytics&#13\;\n     •   UI / 
 UX Design\, User Experience\, Omnichannel Marketing\, and much more!&#13
 \;\n&#13\;\nChallenge traditional ideas\, gain actionable insights\, and
  discover how to thrive and succeed as a marketer in a rapidly evolving 
 digital world. See why people keep coming back year after year to this m
 ust-attend event for any marketer wanting to stay ahead! &#13\;\n&#13\;\
 nRegister and secure your seat today at https://digimarcongreatlakes.com
 .&#13\;\n&quot\;\n\nTags: digital marketing\, marketing\, social media m
 arketing\, digital media\, email marketing\, inbound marketing\, search 
 marketing\, content marketing\, advertising\, Mobile Marketing\, clevela
 nd\, ohio\n\nImported from: http://calagator.org/events/1250482518
URL:https://digimarcongreatlakes.com
SUMMARY:DigiMarCon Great Lakes 2026 - Digital Marketing\, Media and Adver
 tising Conference
LOCATION:The Ritz-Carlton Cleveland Hotel: The Ritz-Carlton Cleveland Hot
 el\, Cleveland OH 44113 United States
SEQUENCE:1
END:VEVENT
